sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant FE as ChatWidget.jsx (React)
    participant RT as genai router (api/routes/genai.py)
    participant EMB as etl.transform
    participant DB as PostgreSQL + pgvector
    participant LLM as Groq LLM (etl.llm.complete)

    U->>FE: ask question q
    FE->>RT: POST /genai/chat {q}
    RT->>EMB: embeddings_available()

    alt embedding model cached
        EMB-->>RT: true
        RT->>EMB: get_embedding(q)
        EMB-->>RT: query vector
        RT->>DB: ORDER BY embedding <=> vector LIMIT 5
    else model not cached (fallback)
        EMB-->>RT: false
        RT->>DB: ORDER BY ts_rank(...) DESC, published_at DESC LIMIT 5
    end
    DB-->>RT: id, title, url, content (top 5 articles)

    RT->>RT: build context [1..5] title + excerpt
    RT->>LLM: complete(system, context + question, model_for("chat"))
    LLM-->>RT: answer text

    RT-->>FE: {answer, sources: [{id, title, url}]}
    FE-->>U: render answer + cited sources
